I'm so glad to hear you're interested in joining #PRS_ORG#!
I'm happy to explain a little more about how #PRS_ORG# works.
#PRS_ORG# is a monthly subscription service which provides access to the world’s largest fitness network.
We partner with over 20,000 studios in cities all over the world to offer both in-person classes as well as livestream options.
Each month you get a certain number of credits to use: the number of classes you can take each cycle depends on your membership plan, and you choose how to use your credits.
You can book classes ranging from yoga to barre to cycling to martial arts.
In many cities, there are also wellness options like massages or haircuts!
When you sign up, you'll also have access to our video on-demand library.
This is included in your membership, and there are tons of videos available.
So if you are wanting to try out a new type of workout or just want to get in a workout at home, I encourage you to check those out.
A few tips to get you up and running #PRS_ORG#:
When you sign up, your membership starts that day.
Your membership will auto-renew every month on that date.
To see the studios near you, check out the search page.
Just click through the individual studio links to access their schedules!
On our website, you'll also be able to see the livestream classes many studios offer.
You'll be able to book classes through our website or app.
The studio will automatically receive your request and save you a spot.
If you can't make it, just be sure to cancel at least 12 hours in advance to avoid fees.
Be sure to check out our Help Center for more information about how #PRS_ORG# works.
If you have any questions, let me know.

You won't have access to class credit pricing without an active membership, but to give you an idea of how our system works, the number of credits needed to book a class is adjusted based on the time you’re booking, what studio you’re visiting, and what time your class is.
While we’re not able to provide a definitive number right now, if there’s a particular studio you’re interested in visiting, we can give you a range of how many credits each class could be.
Just keep in mind that classes do change dynamically and in real time!
